            10.299974,18.5 16.799965,18.5z M22.49997,6.3000488L27.099999,7.9000244 27.099999,30.300049 22.49997,32 0,27.600037 0,10.5z 
            M13.100019,2L13.199994,2.7000122C12.199995,3.1000366,11.299973,3.8000488,11.400009,5L11.400009,7.6000366 10.699998,7.7000122 
